{"tid":803440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西龜慈正邨墮樓 龜殼爆裂受傷","createTime":"2018-09-02T09:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T11:42:08.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c8b13d582ec916c8cc6cfd12558eba1d2f11d5d3","tid":803440,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180902/large/1535872952_8339.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180902%2Flarge%2F1535872952_8339.jpg&h=cac6b4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴西龜被發現在後門位置 (文兆麟攝)<br />\n慈雲山慈正邨正安樓，下午1時許，一隻約一呎長的巴西龜，被發現疑由高處墮下，受傷倒在大廈後門地下，龜殼爆裂，傷勢不輕，警方及愛協人員到場檢視，初步相信案件無可疑，愛協將巴西龜帶走治理，估計巴西龜年約4歲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180902/58636158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180902%2F58636158&d=ZlKfbH7KqDG2KqnAb5yh1sVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=c5b20714\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180902%2F58636158&h=a3053115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180902/58636158</a>"},{"pid":"c8495ffed0528dd4ef1f13904dac5f076b7a8ebc","tid":803440,"uid":199211,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:29:01.000Z","msg":"有無冚親個龜頭"},{"pid":"22105bf219b70deee8d739e3108785d34f5cfad1","tid":803440,"uid":182314,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:29:15.000Z","msg":"烏龜都跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港"},{"pid":"3750ee94a35477969ecda6edc5ba2411943c3c35","tid":803440,"uid":182286,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T09:29:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd88f53c0d42bcf5f2ed2